{"tid":1738903,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"輪迴上有良知善良既人有更大機率投生於好環境","createTime":"2019-11-19T11:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T15:07:04.000Z","uid":189404,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a6d8c3a238effbdfd5c3e1d9ecb995379e0badfc","tid":1738903,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"你仔細辯别內心，係長期陰暗，諗住人地點死踩住黎你自己就可以上位得到更大的利益。<br />\n<br />\n定係光明美好，有慈悲善良之心，能為公義發聲，行動，能愛護幼小。<br />\n<br />\n善人可以升天享福係古今主流宗教都共同宣說既一個道理。<br />\n<br />\n勿謂今日之苦係苦，就算係被虐打痛苦致死，係輪迴路上都只係電光火石之一瞬都及不上。<br />\n彷如一夢。<br />\n<br />\n當然能盡孝道是更好的選擇，故盡量保存自己，不要送頭，用更好的方法去辦事。"},{"pid":"1ac34446fb9b818c53c69dfb7878802ba0a5f4c7","tid":1738903,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:36:55.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"2d661e857f838d39583f802dc17b9f36546d1972","tid":1738903,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:38:00.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"73871800f02e22a2a48856c3d28ca490a6265b96","tid":1738903,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:38:37.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"8997aa667e66eac18a3c4a4ff785a94989f8dda1","tid":1738903,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:40:03.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"f5f836b91da6fe0a692e5abd760370e5194e7b45","tid":1738903,"uid":65091,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:57:59.000Z","msg":"關咩事，因為日本兵上一世殺左人，所以李鳳儀就要死"},{"pid":"7adbf5dcdbc6fb2562a0cadc3295dc1e984aa019","tid":1738903,"uid":218865,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:21:24.000Z","msg":"咁香港人上世一定係黑警"},{"pid":"1c8513148957e5e6e20e356a47b5ca28ff475ce6","tid":1738903,"uid":165115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:10:53.000Z","msg":"誰知下一世一定輪迴做人？<br />\n<br />\n如果係其他（如昆蟲），<br />\n怎定善惡？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e10d257bdd